      "color": "#fcc2d7",
      "language": "javascript",
      "content": "function focusLocationOnCanvas(locationId, { openEditor = true } = {}) { const node = state.nodes.find((n) => String(n.locationId || '').toLowerCase() === id || n.id === `node-${id}`); if (!node) { setStatus(`Нода ${locationId} не найдена на canvas`); return false; } select('node', node.id); state.view.x = rect.width / 2 - (node.x + (node.width || 160) / 2) * state.view.scale; state.view.y = rect.height / 2 - (node.y + (node.height || 100) / 2) * state.view.scale; applyViewTransform(); if (openEditor) openNodeInEditor(node); return true; }\nПоиск ноды по locationId, центрирование viewport, опциональное открытие редактора",
      "x": 1120,
